	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does anyone have any idea why none of the Super Metroid SPCs from SNESmusic.org work with SPC2ROM?  They also don't work with vspcplay.<br /><br /><a href="http://snesmusic.org/v2/profile.php?profile=set&amp;selected=2759" class="postlink">http://snesmusic.org/v2/profile.php?profile=set&amp;selected=2759</a><br /><br />The other SPC sets that I've tried all work fine, but these don't.

		

		</td>
