	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Part of the problem may be the echo. Echo initialization I believe is handled incorrectly by SPC2ROM (I have never used SPC2ROM myself, because I know of a different player that handles .spc files and puts them in .smc files)...<br /><br />_mic made <a href="http://jiggawatt.org/badc0de/spcplayer.htm" class="postlink">spcplayer</a>, which handles .spcs much better (and thus should play Super Metroid SPCs).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


